acceptance_criteria:
1. All four route files exist in src/app/api/auth/
2. POST /api/auth/login accepts JSON body with input, mode, prompt and returns { url } or { error }
3. GET /api/auth/callback-handler reads query params, calls client.callback(), sets session cookie, returns { did }
4. GET /api/auth/session reads cookie, returns { did } or { did: null }
5. POST /api/auth/logout revokes tokens, clears cookie, returns { ok: true }
6. No imports from @atproto/oauth-client-browser
7. No "use client" directives

